name: Morphy Richards DAB CD Boom Box
description: This is the new DAB Boom Box which, on top of smooth curved white plastic design, integrates a CD player with its DAB radio. Two 5 watt speakers and a host of features such as stations presets, FM RDS radio and clock settings complete the package.
